It is the vision of the Mohammed Bin Rashid Center for Leadership Development to create leaders for tomorrows world. To achieve this vision, the Center is launching its flagship program first. This program is designed to be an avant-garde experience that challenges leaders to move outside their comfort zone. It is a journey rather than an event, which will leave the participants being more effective at the end of the program. The curriculum is based on the Mohammed Bin Rashid Al Maktoum Competency Model and is delivered by a consortium of the worlds leading providers of executive education. The modules of the program have been carefully curated and contextualized to be readily applicable to the local context.

We recommend you dedicate 30 minutes to complete this assessment on your computer or phone (not a tablet). pymetrics is designed to be fun and simple, there is no right or wrong answer, and after you finish you will receive a personalized report with insight into your behaviors. For any technical questions relating to accessing pymetrics or completing the assessment, please reach out directly to the pymetrics Helpdesk at support@pymetrics.com.
